-- MOVES-Liontrust Asset hires James Beddall from F&C Investments 
-- 
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 01:00PM EDT
-- None



Sept 26 (Reuters) - Liontrust Asset Management Plc <LIO.L> said it appointed James Beddall co-head of international sales.

Beddall, who has 17 years of experience in international sales, previously worked at F&C Investments, where he was head of international wholesale sales. He will be based in Luxembourg, where Liontrust is in the process of setting up a branch office.